getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取解决的bug
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as bugs from zt_bug t1 where  t1.deleted = '0'  and FIND_IN_SET(t1.id,(select bugs from zt_build where id = ?))

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取完成的需求数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as stories  from zt_story t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and  FIND_IN_SET(t1.id,(select stories from zt_build where id = ?))

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取产生的bug
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(1) as createbugcnt from zt_bug t1 where t1.deleted = '0' and Find_IN_SET(?,(select openedbuild from zt_bug where id = t1.id))
